In this game the player controls the French general and emperor Napoleon Bonaparte. This new release series assumes a kind of "expansion independent" Empire: Total War, but it is a game piece, it is not necessary to have the Empire to install it. The game is located temporarily in the historic campaigns of Napoleonic France, particularly in those who were commanded by Napoleon in person, allowing, as in previous titles, play the imperial campaign strategy shift combined with tactical battles in real time.
